sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant BE as PasswordResetService
  participant ES as EmailService
  participant TX as Transaction Manager
  participant SMTP as SMTP Server

  U->>FE: Forgot password
  FE->>BE: POST /auth/forgot-password
  BE->>BE: Validate user + cooldown
  BE->>BE: Create token (BCrypt hash)
  BE->>TX: Register afterCommit callback
  TX->>TX: Commit transaction
  TX->>ES: Send email (after commit)
  ES->>ES: Build bilingual HTML template
  ES->>SMTP: Send MIME message
  SMTP-->>ES: Delivered
  BE-->>FE: 200 OK
